title: Did Belusi get a picture from Coved 19?
subtitle: Members of Congress were among the first people in the United States to receive the vaccine in 2020.
author: Madison Dapcevich
vclaim: The images published in mid-December 2020 by the Speaker of the United States House of Representatives, Nancy Belusi, a California democracy, showed a COVID-19 vaccine with a needle that was still sealed with its orange hat.
